<br>
Item 1 is on person 1.<br>
<br>
Item 2 is on person 2.<br>
<br>
Person 1 wants Item 3.<br>
<br>
Person 2 hands in item 2 to NPC.<br>
<br>
Person 1 hands in item 1 to NPC after the step above.<br>
<br>
If the faction/level of person 1 fits the prerequisite of the quest, person 1 will receive faction, exp, and item 3.<br>
<br>
in the spirits (for epic), if someone other than the intended druid has a no drop item, he hands it in before the intended druid does.<br>
<br>
Do all these steps in a relative close timing, if not, someone else might come in and do the quest, therefore removing the &quot;item in holding&quot; that the npc has.<br>
<br>
<br>
